# ERP Realtime Sync Standard

## Phase

ERP REALTIME.1 — Supabase Realtime Live Sync (PLANNED — do not implement without explicit Sameer approval)

Full plan: `docs/plans/REALTIME_SYNC_PLAN.md`

---

## The Decision Rule

Before adding a Realtime subscription to any table, ask:
> **"Are two different users ever looking at a list of this data at the same time, and would it confuse them if it's stale?"**

If YES → add Realtime. If NO → do not add it.

---

## Tables That NEED Realtime (Tier 1 — implement first)

| Table | Module | Invalidation helper | List pattern |
|-------|--------|---------------------|--------------|
| `parties` | Party Master | `router.refresh()` | Server-props (B) |
| `party_contacts` | Party child tab | `invalidatePartyContacts(qc, partyId)` | TanStack Query (A) |
| `party_addresses` | Party child tab | `invalidatePartyAddresses(qc, partyId)` | TanStack Query (A) |
| `party_bank_details` | Party child tab | `invalidatePartyBankDetails(qc, partyId)` | TanStack Query (A) |
| `dms_documents` | DMS | `invalidateDmsDocuments(qc)` + `router.refresh()` | Server-props (B) |
| `dms_upload_sessions` | DMS Inbox | `invalidateDmsUploadSessions(qc)` | TanStack Query (A) |
| `employees` | HR | `invalidateHrEmployees(qc)` | Hybrid state (C) |
| `erp_notifications` | Notifications | `invalidateMyNotifications(qc)` | TanStack Query (A) |

## Tables That NEED Realtime (Tier 2 — implement after Tier 1 is stable)

`dms_expiry_reminders`, `dms_renewal_requests`, `hr_leave_requests`, `hr_attendance_summaries`, `hr_candidates`

